column1: ## variable2000 : Top 2000 highly variable genes in Differentiation Atlas.
## randomForestImportance : Association betweeb gene expression  with differentiation learned by randomforest
## heatmapGeneCluster: Gene cluster grouped by K-means in Supplementary Figure 13a.

## gwasTrait: GWAS summary statistics mostly were downloaded from[ GWAS Catalog](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/gwas/).
We used the following data:
[EFO_0007620 ](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/gwas/efotraits/EFO_0007620): volumetric bone mineral density
[EFO_0003882](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/gwas/efotraits/EFO_0003882): osteoporosis
[EFO_0003923]([GWAS Catalog](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/gwas/efotraits/EFO_0003923)):bone density
[EFO_0003931](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/gwas/efotraits/EFO_0003931):bone fracture
[EFO_0007621](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/gwas/efotraits/EFO_0007621): bone-mineral_measure
At the same time, we combined the data provided by an important literature studying osteoporosis: 2019 Nature Genetics [An atlas of genetic influences on osteoporosis in humans and mice](https://www.nature.com/articles/s41588-018-0302-x), tagged as eBMD_2018

## archs_osteoblast,archs_K562,archs_stromal : Data mined from [archs](https://maayanlab.cloud/archs4/download.html). We download mouse osteoblast, stromal cells and K562 cell line, and calculate mean expression.

## nc_known_gene : Genes was obtained from 2021 Nature Communications [Systems genetics in diversity outbred mice inform BMD GWAS and identify determinants of bone strength](https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC8184749/). The author constructed a list of bone genes using GO terms and the Mouse Genome Informatics (MGI) database.

## ncBAN : Genes was obtained from 2021 Nature Communications [Systems genetics in diversity outbred mice inform BMD GWAS and identify determinants of bone strength](https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC8184749/).  BANs were defined as genes connected in our Bayesian networks with more genes in the “known bone gene” list than would be expected by chance

## phylobone : Gene was obtained from 2023  [Phylobone: A comprehensive database of bone extracellular matrix proteins in human and model organisms](https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2023.03.28.534628v2)

## youltenSignature : Signature genes during osteocyte differentiation collected in paper Osteocyte transcriptome mapping identifies a molecular landscape controlling skeletal homeostasis and susceptibility to skeletal disease

## human_skeletal_disorder_youlten : genes assoiciated with skeletal disorders, which is collected in paper Osteocyte transcriptome mapping identifies a molecular landscape controlling skeletal homeostasis and susceptibility to skeletal disease
## Level 2-7 annotation : Marker genes in our Multi-level tree-base annotation system.
